  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       OPENING STATEMENT
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="about-opening">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="opening-inner">
        <div class="opening-quote reveal-up">
          <div class="quote-mark"><i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left"></i></div>
          <blockquote>
            Financial institutions should empower people, businesses, and communities to achieve more — not just manage transactions.
          </blockquote>
          <cite>— Sterling Crest Union, Founding Charter, 2004</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="opening-text reveal-up d1">
          <p>In an era when banking was becoming increasingly complex, detached, and fee-driven, a group of visionary financial experts, economists, and technology innovators came together with a shared mission: to create a banking institution built on trust, innovation, and global accessibility.</p>
          <p>That mission has never wavered. Twenty years and three million customers later, it has only grown stronger.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       JOURNEY TIMELINE
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="timeline-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal-up">
        <span class="section-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-timeline"></i> Our Journey</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">A <em>Story</em> Written Across Decades</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Every milestone is a chapter. Every chapter, a promise kept.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <!-- 2004 -->
        <div class="timeline-item tl-left reveal-tl">
          <div class="tl-dot dot-teal"><span>2004</span></div>
          <div class="tl-card tl-teal">
            <div class="tl-img-wrap">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1444653614773-995cb1ef9efa?w=600&q=80" alt="Founding" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-body">
              <span class="tl-year-tag tl-tag-teal">Year One</span>
              <h3>A Vision Born from Trust</h3>
              <p>Sterling Crest Union opened its doors as a regional financial cooperative serving entrepreneurs, families, and emerging businesses. From day one, we distinguished ourselves through personalized service, transparent practices, and an uncompromising commitment to helping clients build lasting financial security.</p>
              <div class="tl-stat-row">
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>1</strong><span>Branch</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>12</strong><span>Staff Members</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>3,400</strong><span>First Customers</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2007 -->
        <div class="timeline-item tl-right reveal-tl d1">
          <div class="tl-dot dot-violet"><span>2007</span></div>
          <div class="tl-card tl-violet">
            <div class="tl-img-wrap">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366754035-f200968a6e72?w=600&q=80" alt="Expansion" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-body">
              <span class="tl-year-tag tl-tag-violet">Expansion</span>
              <h3>Crossing the First Border</h3>
              <p>Recognizing an opportunity to bridge financial gaps across continents, Sterling Crest Union established its first international office. Strategic partnerships with global payment networks allowed us to offer seamless cross-border banking while maintaining the personal touch that defined our origins.</p>
              <div class="tl-stat-row">
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>8</strong><span>Countries</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>220</strong><span>Staff</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>85K</strong><span>Customers</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2011 -->
        <div class="timeline-item tl-left reveal-tl">
          <div class="tl-dot dot-gold"><span>2011</span></div>
          <div class="tl-card tl-gold">
            <div class="tl-img-wrap">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?w=600&q=80" alt="Technology" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-body">
              <span class="tl-year-tag tl-tag-gold">Innovation</span>
              <h3>The Digital Revolution Begins</h3>
              <p>Rather than viewing technological change as a challenge, we embraced it as a catalyst for growth. Heavy investment in digital infrastructure, cybersecurity, and AI-driven fraud prevention systems led to the launch of our first secure online banking platform — setting a new industry benchmark.</p>
              <div class="tl-stat-row">
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>34</strong><span>Countries</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>1.2K</strong><span>Staff</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>420K</strong><span>Customers</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2016 -->
        <div class="timeline-item tl-right reveal-tl d1">
          <div class="tl-dot dot-coral"><span>2016</span></div>
          <div class="tl-card tl-coral">
            <div class="tl-img-wrap">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559027615-cd4628902d4a?w=600&q=80" alt="Community" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-body">
              <span class="tl-year-tag tl-tag-coral">Purpose</span>
              <h3>Investing in Communities</h3>
              <p>Growth was never measured solely by assets. We launched the Sterling Crest Foundation — funding educational initiatives, small-business financing, affordable housing support, and financial literacy campaigns. Thousands of entrepreneurs launched businesses. Students accessed opportunities. Communities were transformed.</p>
              <div class="tl-stat-row">
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>$240M</strong><span>Community Invested</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>82</strong><span>Countries</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>1.1M</strong><span>Customers</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2020 -->
        <div class="timeline-item tl-left reveal-tl">
          <div class="tl-dot dot-teal"><span>2020</span></div>
          <div class="tl-card tl-teal">
            <div class="tl-img-wrap">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563986768609-322da13575f3?w=600&q=80" alt="Mobile Banking" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-body">
              <span class="tl-year-tag tl-tag-teal">Mobile-First</span>
              <h3>Banking in Every Pocket</h3>
              <p>The launch of our award-winning mobile platform marked a new era. Instant transfers, biometric security, AI-powered spending insights, real-time FX, and investment tools — all in one beautifully designed app. Downloaded over 5 million times in the first year alone.</p>
              <div class="tl-stat-row">
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>5M+</strong><span>App Downloads</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>120</strong><span>Countries</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>2.1M</strong><span>Customers</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Today -->
        <div class="timeline-item tl-right reveal-tl d1">
          <div class="tl-dot dot-violet today-dot"><span>Today</span></div>
          <div class="tl-card tl-violet tl-today">
            <div class="tl-img-wrap">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606189934846-a527add8a77b?w=600&q=80" alt="Global Banking" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-body">
              <span class="tl-year-tag tl-tag-violet">Present Day</span>
              <h3>A Global Financial Institution</h3>
              <p>Today, Sterling Crest Union serves millions of customers worldwide — from individual account holders and small businesses to multinational corporations and institutional investors. With a global network of professionals and advanced financial platforms, we continue to connect people, businesses, and opportunities across international markets.</p>
              <div class="tl-stat-row">
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>3M+</strong><span>Customers</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>180+</strong><span>Countries</span></div>
                <div class="tl-stat"><strong>$48B+</strong><span>Assets</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

